	      <supportDesc>
		<support>
		  <p>Sculptured memorial: a couple is depicted
		     within a bordered panel with two attendants 
		     behind. The left side figure holds up a vase and
		     casket in both his hands, and on the right side 
		     is a chauri bearer. Dimensions:
		  <dimensions unit="cm">
		    <height>50</height>
		    <width>32</width>
		    <depth>15</depth>
		  </dimensions>.</p>
